body_html: We might need your help debugging this. Usually errors are reported through and ErrorReporter and the default reporter just prints to stderr. In your case, it looks like something is going wrong but not being properly reported. If you could trace the code in AllocateTensors to see what can be going wrong, great. Otherwise we might need access to your model.
